Definition: a detailed plan or explanation to guide you in setting standards or determining a course of action
Example: the president said he had a road map for normalizing relations with Vietnam
Synonyms: guideline, plan, noun, communication, guidance, a, detailed, or, explanation, to, guide, you, in, setting, standards, determining, course, of, action, the, president, said, he, had, road, map, for, normalizing, relations, with, Vietnam
Category: noun.cognition
